llvm-toolchain-snapshot (1:7~svn330801-1~exp2) experimental; urgency=medium

  * d/p/force-gcc-header-obj.diff Fix the detection of the objc path
  * Add python-yaml as dep for clang-tidy (Closes: #890514)
